lisp_spec:
(task
  (name "findSecret")
  (signature ( (text str) ) str)
  (constraints
    (constraint "The input text must contain the secret word.")
    (constraint "The secret word is case-sensitive and appears at the very end of the text.")
  )
  (goal
    (description "Read the provided text and find the secret word mentioned at the very end. Return only that word.")
    (rule "The function should return the secret word if it exists in the text, otherwise return an empty string.")
    (return "The secret word found at the end of the text, or an empty string if not found.")
  )
)
